209
00:15:00,060 --> 00:15:04,060
There are a lot of times when people ask,
"Why is g0v decentralized?"

210
00:15:04,060 --> 00:15:06,740
Or, "Why is g0v polycentric?"

211
00:15:06,740 --> 00:15:09,900
It's a very important question,
and a very interesting one.

212
00:15:09,900 --> 00:15:11,900
Everyone has their own opinion,

213
00:15:11,900 --> 00:15:16,180
and everyone has their own perspective
when answering this question.

214
00:15:16,180 --> 00:15:22,900
What I think is why is g0v polycentric
is because democracy is also polycentric.

215
00:15:22,900 --> 00:15:26,900
In a democracy, like South Korea
or Taiwan,

216
00:15:26,900 --> 00:15:29,340
there are a lot
of different kinds of people,

217
00:15:29,340 --> 00:15:31,900
and people have all kinds
of different opinions.

218
00:15:31,900 --> 00:15:35,900
And people form different groups,
different organizations,

219
00:15:35,900 --> 00:15:40,220
different networks, and every different
networks or different groups

220
00:15:40,220 --> 00:15:45,620
does different things, and because we
have basic freedoms, civic liberties,

221
00:15:45,620 --> 00:15:50,780
we're doing
what we want to do,

222
00:15:50,780 --> 00:15:52,780
and we have the freedom to associate,

223
00:15:52,780 --> 00:15:56,860
we have the freedom to assemble,
and we have the freedom of speech.

224
00:15:56,860 --> 00:15:59,420
And these kind of values, these values

225
00:15:59,420 --> 00:16:02,960
are the values that
the g0v community supports.

226
00:16:04,760 --> 00:16:06,880
So, what I think is g0v

227
00:16:06,880 --> 00:16:12,530
could be seen as a mini version.
or a shadow version of

228
00:16:12,530 --> 00:16:16,640
the larger democracy or
society that we live in today.

229
00:16:16,640 --> 00:16:22,660
And g0v is also a very good place to
discuss or even experiment

230
00:16:22,660 --> 00:16:25,280
different kinds of democratic methods.

231
00:16:29,280 --> 00:16:34,330
So a community like g0v
is very decentralized or polycentric,

232
00:16:34,680 --> 00:16:39,920
which also means that
it needs policies and mechanisms

233
00:16:39,920 --> 00:16:43,640
