or to support its polycentrism.

234
00:16:44,950 --> 00:16:51,060
I think a community like g0v
needs policies and mechanisms

235
00:16:51,060 --> 00:16:55,220
to maintain its polycentric nature

236
00:16:55,540 --> 00:17:00,880
to prevent abuse--
to express its many selves

237
00:17:01,120 --> 00:17:06,360
meaning everyone is
everyone is a g0v contributor.

