00:21:00,080 --> 00:21:02,600
It actually--
it actually just lists out

291
00:21:02,600 --> 00:21:06,820
different kinds of way to
identify yourself as someone

292
00:21:06,820 --> 00:21:15,200
who is connected or who--
who acknowledges the community.

293
00:21:15,200 --> 00:21:19,740
This first one is contributor,
