302
00:21:53,600 --> 00:21:55,600
but the term 'member'

303
00:21:55,600 --> 00:21:59,600
just suggests that some people are inside,
some people are outside,

304
00:21:59,600 --> 00:22:01,800
but it's actually
more complicated than that.

