00:22:38,780 --> 00:22:43,100
how g0v-ers engage with--
sort of, the world.

312
00:22:43,100 --> 00:22:46,900
Things are-- things that are not communal.

313
00:22:46,900 --> 00:22:48,900
Other hierarchical organizations.

314
00:22:48,900 --> 00:22:55,440
Or other people that have not heard
