315
00:22:59,240 --> 00:23:05,240
It lists out different ways
of engaging with the world.

316
00:23:05,240 --> 00:23:07,840
This one is a panel discussion.

317
00:23:07,840 --> 00:23:09,840
Maybe a press conference.

318
00:23:09,840 --> 00:23:11,840
How do you-- how do you--

319
00:23:11,840 --> 00:23:15,840
what is the best way to sort of
navigate those situations.

